algorithms.trees

Class TDP_Anyk_Iterator

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithms.trees.TDP_Anyk_Iterator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TDP_Part, TDP_Recursive, Tree_Batch

    public abstract class TDP_Anyk_Iterator
extends Object
    A ranked enumeration algorithm for a T-DP problem specified by a TDP_Problem_Instance object. It is implemented as an iterator that is first initialized and then the method get_next() returns the next best T-DP solution in ranked order. This is an abstract class: to instantiate it, a subclass that implements get_next() must be provided.

    IMPORTANT: Before using this class, TDP_Problem_Instance.bottom_up() must have already been run on the T-DP instance.
    Author:
    Nikolaos Tziavelis
